-- Turkey Should Join Adriatic Gas Link to Access Balkans: TAP
-- B y   O n u r   A n t
-- 2013-07-10T12:16:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-10/turkey-should-join-adriatic-gas-link-to-access-balkans-tap.html
Trans-Adriatic Pipeline consortium
has repeatedly asked  Turkey  to join TAP project, TAP Turkey
representative Cenk Pala said today in televised interview on
Bloomberg HT.
* TAP stake would give Turkey access to Balkan states, has
strategic value for Ankara: Pala
* NOTE: Azerbaijan selected TAP to send 10 bcm of natural gas
annually to Europe
* NOTE: TAP, developed by  Statoil ASA (STL) , EON Ruhrgas and EGL AG,
will ship Azeri gas to Italy from Turkish border  To contact the reporter on this story:
Onur Ant in Ankara at 
